---
title: Carb Smart Chicken Tenders Bulgur Bowls with DIY Jalapeño-Ranch Dressing
description: Jalapeño-ranch dressing steals the show in this quick and well-balanced bowl. Smoky, baked chicken pairs perfectly with creamy ranch, while lemony bulgur brings brightness to every bite!

